data.description: Inviting Fully Furnished 4-Bedroom, 3-Bathroom Pool & Spa Home    Welcome to a delightful retreat in Davenport, Florida! This charming property offers you 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a host of features that will make you feel right at home.    Key Features:    Two Master Suites: Perfect for accommodating vacation rentals or large families, this home boasts two master suites, providing ample space and privacy.  Turnkey Convenience: You won't need to worry about furnishing your new home; it comes fully furnished and ready for you to enjoy from day one.  Upgraded Interiors: Step inside to discover numerous updates, from fresh flooring to a recently painted interior. This home is truly turnkey and move-in ready.  Outdoor Oasis: As you step outside, a generously sized covered lanai welcomes you, leading to a south-facing pool and spa. The rear area is incredibly private, offering a serene tropical-like oasis for your relaxation.  Picture-Perfect Setting: Imagine yourself on the spacious deck, soaking in the sun with a refreshing drink in hand, while gazing upon your very own tropical paradise.  Convenience Meets Location: With major attractions, shopping, and dining just a short drive away, you'll find yourself in close proximity to Walt Disney World, SeaWorld, Universal, and all the attractions that make Orlando famous. Everything is within a 15-30 minute drive, so you won't need to search further for your perfect home.    Motivated Seller: The seller is eager to make a deal. Don't miss this opportunity to own a beautiful and fully-furnished home in a prime location. Make your offer today and start enjoying the Florida lifestyle!
